	Well, well![BR]
	[Pause 10]Our dear little Goombario is[BR]
	helping out the great Mario![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I'm so proud![HEART][BR]
	[Pause 10]I'm going to tell Dad and[BR]
	Goompa![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Mario, you must come over to our[BR]
	house again someday![Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0B9
{
