}

#message:06:0C6
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Do you believe in good faith?[BR]
	[Pause 15][PrintRising]Haw haw! [SaveColor][Color:1F]Bower[RestoreColor] sure doesn't![/fx][BR]
	[Pause 15]After all,[Pause 3] he's deceiving the[BR]
	people with his lust.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	His coercion is corrupting[BR]
	not just [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Heaven[RestoreColor], but your[BR]
	world as well.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
