	been saved, but without all[BR]
	seven, we don't stand a chance.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	We may not be draco spheres[BR]
	or chaotic gems, [Pause 8]but we will[BR]
	put in the effort to enable[BR]
	your success.[Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0C7
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Whatever. Ignore that idiot.[BR]
	[Pause 15]I don't usually lose my composure,[BR]
	but my duty as a [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Deity[RestoreColor][BR]
	is very important to me.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
