#message:06:0CA
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Woah ho! Who do we have here?[BR]
	[Pause 10]A [SaveColor][Color:09]Love Deity[RestoreColor]?[Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0CB
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]............[Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0CC
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Not the talkative type, eh?[BR]
	[Pause 10]I guess that's alright.[Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0CD
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star][DitherFade percent=65]Not so loud![BR]
	[Pause 10]I want to keep my identity[BR]
	confidential okay?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	This town can't know I was[BR]
	ever here. Got that?[Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0CE
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star][PrintRising]Y-yessir![/fx][Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0CF
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Good.[BR]
	[Pause 5]And with that...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Size 32][Down 16] [WAve][STAR][STAR][STAR][STAR] [HEART][HEART][HEART][HEART][Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0D0
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]I almost forgot![BR]
	[Pause 8]It's taboo for Love Deities to[BR]
	be noticed by humans.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Enough of that then.[BR]
	[Pause 10]You're still keeping that[BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:04]Star of China[RestoreColor] safe, right?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Well... [Pause 5]that pendant can only[BR]
	be open by the princess of[BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:09]Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I think I have a sneaking [BR]
	suspicion on who the princess is,[BR]
	[Pause 5]but that isn't relevant to you.[BR][Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0D1
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]Let's just say...[BR]
	[Pause 12]I've been working with her very[BR]
	closely now for some time.[Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0D2
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]...But still...[BR]
	[Pause 6]What sort of business would[BR]
	Bower have with [SaveColor][Color:09]Doki Doki Castle[RestoreColor]?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	It doesn't make sense...[Pause 8] yet.[BR]
	[Pause 15]I'll be doing more research[BR]
	on the matter.[Wait][End]
}

#message:06:0D3
{
	[Style Right]
	[Voice Star]I have also uncovered that the[BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:04]Star of China[RestoreColor] holds secrets to[BR]
	my past, but I can't say for[BR]
	certain until we open it.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Oh well,[Pause 5] that will be a mystery[BR]
	worth finding out.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I have to retreat to HQ for[BR]
	now, Mario.[Pause 10] See ya.[Wait][End]
}

